"Choose which languages the selector offers your pilots. English is the "
"source language and is always available. Turning a language on here reveals "
"it in the language menu; the app stays English-default until a pilot picks "
"another."
msgstr ""
"Выберите, какие языки селектор предлагает вашим пилотам. Английский — "
